<h1>
 Media appearances
</h1>
<p>John speaks with the press frequently, and is quoted and interviewed on a regular basis.
Representative quotes and interviews include:</p>
<ul>
<li><p><a target=notjrl href="http://news.com.com/Finding+a+way+to+fry+spam/2008-1032_3-5164246.html"><i>Finding a way to fry spam</i></a> (February 24, 2004)<br>
Extensive interview on CNet.
Some of the quotes got a little fractured, but the gist is easy enough to follow.</p></li> 
<li><p><a target=notjrl href="http://www.pcworld.com/news/article/0,aid,118816,00.asp"><i>Lycos, Spammers Trade Blows</i></a><br>
Quoted in PC World article on Lycos Europe gimmick purporting to
counterattack spam web sites.</p></li>
<li><p><a target=notjrl href="http://story.news.yahoo.com/news?tmpl=story2&u=/ap/20041114/ap_on_hi_te/inside_spamming"><i>Trial Shows How Spammers Operate</i></a><br>
Quoted in syndicated Associated Press article about the nation's first criminal spamming
trial in which he was an expert witness for the prosecution.
<li><p><a target=notjrl href="http://www.entrepreneur.com/mag/article/0,1539,316027,00.html">Entrepreneur Magazine</a> (July 2004, p. 28)<br>
