<H1>
  Scheduling a speaking engagement
</H1>
<P>
Contact John directly at <tt>speak&#64;johnlevine.com</tt> to ask about possible
topics and availability.
</p>
<P>
Contact his speaking agent <A HREF="mailto:LesT@leighbureau.com">The
Leigh Bureau</A>, by e-mail or telephone 1-908-253-8600, or fax 1-908-253-8601,
for terms and costs. He generally does book signing events at no charge beyond expenses; book
stores should contact him directly. 
</p>
